## Performance Benchmarks

| Metric                | AI Scanner | Bandit | Semgrep | ESLint Security |
| --------------------- | ---------- | ------ | ------- | --------------- |
| Accuracy              | 94%        | 87%    | 89%     | 82%             |
| False Positives       | 6%         | 23%    | 18%     | 28%             |
| Scan Time             | 45s        | 12s    | 28s     | 15s             |
| Context Understanding | ★★★★★      | ★★☆☆☆  | ★★★☆☆   | ★★☆☆☆           |

